Uniform Housing Code – Provisions not adopted.
The following provisions of the Uniform Housing Code, 1997 Edition, are not
adopted as part of the Kern County Housing Code and shall not apply thereto:
Section 203 Housing Advisory and Appeals Board;
Section 302 Fees;
Section 303 Inspection.

